vote.title: Authorize a five-year service contract, with three one-year renewal options, for janitorial services for the Department of Aviation - Flagship Airport Services, Inc. in the amount of $1,871,365.50 and Andrews Building Service, Inc. in the amount of $653,762.04, most advantageous proposers of eighteen - Not to exceed $2,525,127.54 - Financing:  Aviation Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
